Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
