Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
