Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让地球的后裔为之倾倒{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}over the hearts and dreams of the scions of Earth.{\r}
