Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是首批人类探险家将是开路先锋{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But the first human explorers will just be blazing the trail...{\r}
