Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在这个空间殖民地生存的所需的一切{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}everything we'll need to survive in this space colony of the future.{\r}
