Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.19,0:30:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是为人类居民提供能量远不是简单的事情{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}fueling the human settlers is not nearly as straightforward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.24,0:31:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}挨饿将会是笼罩移民的持续阴影{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Starvation will be a constant shadow looming over the colonists...{\r}
