Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.84,0:31:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对于我们未来的无畏的火星移民来说{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For our fearless Mars colonists of the future...{\r}
