Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.81,0:31:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都证明是艰巨的挑战{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}proves to be a daunting hardship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.85,0:31:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所要对付的有可能是最基本的需求 食物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Take what may be the most basic need of all--food.{\r}
