Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.57,0:31:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从地球送往火星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from Earth's surface to Mars' surface.{\r}
