Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.84,0:31:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}即便那样 火星上种植不是便当的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Even then, growing plants on Mars isn't as easy...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.63,0:32:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}简单播下种子灌溉就行了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as simply sticking a seed in the ground and watering it.{\r}
