Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.25,0:32:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他们不能依赖火星土壤来培育地球上植物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They cannot rely on Mars' soil to nurture plants from Earth.{\r}
