Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.84,0:32:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们同时也在温室里种植它们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We also grow them in a greenhouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.18,0:32:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就是地球上的温室{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is what greenhouses are like on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.01,0:32:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们建在地面上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're located on the surface of the ground...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.93,0:32:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}利用天然的太阳辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they use natural solar radiation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.52,0:32:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}全年运作 没有来自太空的陨石{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they operate year-round without danger from meteorites...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.06,0:32:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}和电离辐射的危险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or ionizing radiation from space.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.57,0:33:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在火星上 温室是控制作物的培育室{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On Mars, the greenhouse is a controlled growth chamber...{\r}
