Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.66,0:40:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其质量约20亿吨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}would have a mass of about two billion tons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.37,0:40:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其重量等于2万艘尼米兹级航母{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's equal in weight to 20,000 Nimitz-class aircraft carriers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.04,0:40:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}此等规模的小行星可能包含着镍 钴 铂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}An asteroid of this size could contain enough nickel, cobalt, and platinum...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.30,0:40:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其价值超过1500亿美元{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to be valued at over $150 billion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.80,0:40:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这只是颗不大的小行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And this is just a small asteroid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有些巨石的直径达到了行星的规模{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some monster rocks approach the dimensions of a real planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.90,0:40:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}开采小行星是史无前例的事情{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mining an asteroid is something that we've never done before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.19,0:40:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不管怎样 或许会有办法{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}However, perhaps there are ways...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.15,0:40:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}钻入小行星的土地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in which to dig into the asteroid's soil...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.57,0:40:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们并不认为会有多大的难度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which we don't think is going to be that hard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.82,0:40:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个办法就是激光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One way is laser beams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.53,0:40:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以用高科技来产生激光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We can use high technology to create laser beams...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.29,0:40:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}直接切割小行星的物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that'll slice right through the asteroid material.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.75,0:41:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是要在真空的太空里掏空一块巨石{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But hollowing out a megaton rock in the airless void of space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.22,0:41:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}决不是一件轻而易举的任务{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is by no means an easy proposition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.47,0:41:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小行星带里的辐射相当厉害{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Radiation in the asteroid belt is quite harsh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.10,0:41:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}尤其是因为{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}especially because Jupiter itself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.94,0:41:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}木星自身释放出大量的辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}releases an enormous amount of radiation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.82,0:41:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就意味着小行星上的矿工{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This means that miners on the surface of an asteroid belt...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能不得不生活在小行星的地下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}may have to live underground inside the asteroid itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那会给他们一些保护{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That would give them some protection...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.41,0:41:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}免遭太阳的辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from the radiation from the Sun...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.46,0:41:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}木星的辐射以及外太空的辐射{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}radiation from Jupiter, and radiation from outer space...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.79,0:41:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}依靠生活在小行星的地下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}by living inside the asteroid itself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.26,0:41:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许这是最好留给铁人们的活计{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Maybe this is a job better left to men of iron.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.39,0:41:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为小行星带太遥远了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because the asteroid belt is so distant...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.85,0:41:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}约有3亿英里远{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}perhaps 300 million miles away...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.69,0:41:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可能不得不用上机器人了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we may have to use robots.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.81,0:41:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}机器人相对较为便宜{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Robots are going to be relatively cheap...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.31,0:41:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们无需生命的支持{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they don't require life support...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.19,0:42:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们可以有去无回{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they don't have to come back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.46,0:42:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对于首批星际移民来说{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For the first interplanetary colony...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.71,0:42:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}类人机器人 与它们的宇航员伙伴一道工作{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}humanoid robots, working together with their astronaut partners...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.30,0:42:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是将风险降到最小 最大限度生存的唯一途径{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is the only way to minimize risk and maximize survival.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.56,0:42:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}火星生活的方方面面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In every way, daily life on Mars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.14,0:42:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都将是终极冒险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will be the ultimate extreme adventure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.53,0:42:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你早晨醒来 已经多出了一个小时的睡眠{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You get up in the morning, you've had an hour extra sleep...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.20,0:42:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会跳下床 因为只有一半的重力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you bound out of bed because there's half the gravity...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.74,0:42:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后你穿衣外出{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}then you suit up to go outside...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.37,0:42:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为你有一个小时的本职工作{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because you have an hour of duty, checking on the robots...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.37,0:42:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}检查维持生命的机器人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that keep life possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.50,0:43:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后你掉头回家 止步在一个山坡上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then on your way home, you stop on a ridge...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你环顾整个山谷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and you look across the valley into the canyons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.34,0:43:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你仰望火星的天空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And you look up at the Martian sky...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.09,0:43:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}繁星闪烁 蔚为壮观{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with the amazing sight of stars twinkling through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.19,0:43:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}探索火星表面将会是精彩的冒险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Exploring the surface of Mars is going to be a fantastic adventure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.03,0:43:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}景观之美 无与伦比{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There are landscapes that are of unimaginable beauty...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}叹为观止{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}some completely alien to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.20,0:43:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}无穷无尽的地貌{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There are thousands and thousands of kilometers...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.66,0:43:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}向四面八方延展{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of terrain to cover in every direction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.75,0:43:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里将是科学家梦寐以求的仙境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's going to be a fantastic wonderland for scientists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.97,0:43:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}活跃在火星殖民地上的这种景色 眼下还是幻想{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This view of a working colony on Mars is, for now, fiction...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.10,0:43:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}据称是21世纪的科学{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}informed by the best of 21st century science.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.36,0:44:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是十有八九 有朝一日{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But in all likelihood, one day...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.11,0:44:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在盘踞在外星土地上的穹顶城市里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in domed cities entrenched in alien soil...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.83,0:44:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}并不是那些小绿人{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}rather than being little green men...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.66,0:44:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们的天上邻居将属于我们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}our celestial neighbors will be us.{\r}
